text:
Producer! I'm all dressed up!
How does it look?

You look great!
Any concerns about the fit or comfort?

None at all!
It's amazing how we all match!

And I really love the design!
Just wearing it boosts my mood!

Yeah, and you know,
wearing this new outfit...

It made me feel nostalgic...
Being part of 283 makes me happy...

That's right.
I'm glad to see Meguru wearing this outfit.

Hey, hey, Producer!
I want to do lots of different jobs in this outfit!

Like concerts, events, handshake meetings...
Anything, really! Just lots of them!
